.TH PKGCHECKMISSING 1 "PKGMAIN-#VERSION# Manual"

.SH NAME
pkgcheckmissing - check for missing files

.SH SYNOPSIS
pkgcheckmissing

.SH DESCRIPTION
pkgcheckmissing checks for missing files comparing the
installed files on the system with the ones listed in
the pkgutils database.
.PP
This script requires \fBpkginfo\fR(8).
